    <title>Geothermal Research Fellowship Opportunity at U. of Nevada, Reno</title> 
    <link href="http://www.iris.edu/hq/internship/news/entry/geothermal_geothermal_research_fellowship_opportunity_at_u._of_nevada_"> 
